# OpenAI Configuration Example
# 
# Option 1: Set as environment variable (recommended for production)
# Windows: set OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
# Linux/Mac: export OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
#
# Option 2: Set as JVM system property when starting Tomcat
# Add to CATALINA_OPTS: -Dopenai.apiKey=your-api-key-here
#
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
